The paper deals with image obfuscation and privacy preservation, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The proposed method involves the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper introduces a collaborative training scheme, which is a type of adversarial training commonly used in generative models, and thus, the paper may also be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
